%%{init: {"theme":"neutral"}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> Draft : addLine() / créer panier

    Draft --> Validated : validate()<br/>[stock dispo &amp;&amp; lignes &gt; 0]
    Draft --> Cancelled : abort()

    Validated --> PaymentPending : submitPayment()
    PaymentPending --> Paid : paymentAccepted()
    PaymentPending --> PaymentFailed : paymentDeclined()
    PaymentFailed --> PaymentPending : retry()
    PaymentFailed --> Cancelled : timeout()

    Paid --> Preparing : pickAndPack()
    Preparing --> Shipped : ship()
    Shipped --> Delivered : deliveryConfirmed()
    Delivered --> Closed : after 30 days<br/>(fenêtre retour close)

    Delivered --> ReturnRequested : customerReturn()
    ReturnRequested --> Refunded : refund()
    Refunded --> Closed

    Cancelled --> [*]
    Closed --> [*]

    note right of Paid
      Insertion effective dans
      commande &amp; ligne_commande
      → consommé par fait_ventes
    end note
